eya_def_tools.data_models.energy_assessment.EnergyAssessment
Energy assessment details and results.
Attributes: gross_eya_process (AssessmentProcessDescription): Specification of the model used to calculate the gross EYA estimates. gross_eya_results (list[Result]): Gross energy production predictions in GWh. plant_performance_loss_categories (list[PlantPerformanceCategory]): Plant performance loss assessment categories including results. energy_uncertainty_categories (list[EnergyUncertaintyCategory]): Energy related uncertainty assessment categories including results. net_eya_results (list[Result]): Net energy production predictions in GWh, including overall uncertainties and results at different confidence levels.

eya_def_tools.data_models.energy_uncertainty.EnergyUncertaintyCategory
Category of an energy related uncertainty assessment.

eya_def_tools.data_models.plant_performance.PlantPerformanceCategory
Plant performance loss assessment category.
Attributes: label (PlantPerformanceCategoryLabel(StrEnum)): Label of the plant performance loss category. description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None. subcategories (list[PlantPerformanceSubcategory]): Plant performance loss assessment subcategories that fall under the category. The subcategory objects include details and results at the subcategory level. category_results (list[Result]): Plant performance assessment category result(s) as dimensionless loss factors (efficiencies).

eya_def_tools.data_models.process_description.AssessmentProcessDescription
Description of a process used in an energy yield assessment.
Attributes: name (str): Name of the process or model. description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None.

eya_def_tools.data_models.result.Result
Collection of results a quantity along specific dimensions.
Attributes: label (Optional[str]): Label of the results. Default is None. description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None. assessment_period (Optional[AssessmentPeriod(StrEnum)]): Period of or in time that has been assessed and for which the results are applicable. Default is None. dimensions (Optional[tuple[ResultsDimension(StrEnum), ...]]): Dimensions along which the results are binned (all result values in the same results object must have the same dimensions). Default is None. statistics (list[ResultStatistic]): List of result statistic objects that each include result values for a specific statistic type.

eya_def_tools.data_models.plant_performance.PlantPerformanceSubcategory
Plant performance loss assessment subcategory.
Attributes: label (PlantPerformanceSubcategoryLabel(StrEnum)): Label of the plant performance loss subcategory. description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None. basis (AssessmentBasis(StrEnum)): Basis of plant performance loss subcategory assessment. The basis describes the level of detail of the calculation or estimate used in the assessment of the subcategory. variability (TimeVariabilityType(StrEnum)): Considered variability in the plant performance loss subcategory. assessment_process_descriptions (Optional[list[AssessmentProcessDescription]]): Description of calculation processes used in the assessment of the plant performance loss subcategory. Default is None. elements (Optional[list[PlantPerformanceSubcategoryElement]]): Plant performance loss assessment elements that fall under the subcategory. The element objects include details and results at the element level. A breakdown of plant performance loss subcategories into elements is optional and can be included only for a subset of the subcategories, as relevant. Whereas the categories and subcategories are fixed, the user may freely define element labels. Default is None. subcategory_results (list[Result]): Plant performance assessment subcategory result(s) as dimensionless loss factors (efficiencies).

eya_def_tools.data_models.result.ResultStatistic
Result values for one specific statistic type.
Attributes: description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None. statistic_type (StatisticType(StrEnum)): Type of statistic in the results component. values (UnionType[float, list[tuple[tuple[UnionType[float, int, str], ...], float]]]): Result as a single number or values at coordinates.

eya_def_tools.data_models.plant_performance.PlantPerformanceSubcategoryElement
Plant performance loss assessment subcategory element.
Attributes: label (str): Label of the plant performance loss subcategory element. description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None. basis (AssessmentBasis(StrEnum)): Basis of plant performance loss subcategory element assessment. The basis describes the level of detail of the calculation or estimate used in the assessment of the element. variability (TimeVariabilityType(StrEnum)): Considered variability in the plant performance loss subcategory element. is_independent (bool): Whether the plant performance loss subcategory element is independent of all other elements. Default is True. assessment_process_descriptions (Optional[list[AssessmentProcessDescription]]): Description of calculation processes used in the assessment of the plant performance loss subcategory element. Default is None. element_results (list[Result]): Plant performance assessment subcategory element result(s) as dimensionless loss factors (efficiencies).

eya_def_tools.data_models.scenario.Scenario
Single unique energy yield assessment scenario.
Attributes: scenario_id (Optional[str]): Unique identifier of the scenario. Default is None. label (str): Label of the scenario. description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None. is_main_scenario (Optional[bool]): Whether or not this is the main scenario in the report. Default is None. operational_lifetime_length_years (ConstrainedFloatValue): Number of years of project operational lifetime. wind_farms (list[WindFarmConfiguration]): List of all wind farms included in the scenario. turbine_wind_resource_assessment (TurbineWindResourceAssessment): Wind resource assessment at the turbine locations. energy_assessment (EnergyAssessment): Energy assessment details and results, including gross energy, plant performance, net energy and uncertainties.

eya_def_tools.data_models.wind_farm.WindFarmConfiguration
A collection of wind turbines considered as one unit (plant).
Attributes: name (str): Name of the wind farm. label (Optional[str]): Abbreviated label of the wind farm. Default is None. description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None. turbines (list[TurbineConfiguration]): List of specifications for constituent turbines. relevance (WindFarmRelevance(StrEnum)): The relevance of the wind farm for the assessment. operational_lifetime_start_date (Optional[date]): Operational lifetime start date (format YYYY-MM-DD). Default is None. operational_lifetime_end_date (Optional[date]): Operational lifetime end date (format YYYY-MM-DD). Default is None. wind_farm_restrictions (Optional[list[OperationalRestriction]]): List of operational restrictions at the wind farm level. Default is None.

eya_def_tools.data_models.wind_resource.TurbineWindResourceAssessment
Wind resource assessment at the turbine locations.
Attributes: wind_resource_assessment_id_reference (str): The ID of the wind resource assessment on which the turbine wind resource assessment is based. This must refer to an ID of a wind resource assessment included at the top level of the EYA DEF. The schema requires that a turbine wind resource assessment is based on only one wind resource assessment. description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None. wind_spatial_modelling_processes (list[AssessmentProcessDescription]): Wind spatial modelling processes used in the assessment. results (TurbineWindResourceAssessmentResults): Results of the wind resource assessment at the turbine location(s). wind_uncertainty_categories (list[WindUncertaintyCategory]): Wind related uncertainty assessment categories including results.

eya_def_tools.data_models.wind_farm.OperationalRestriction
Specifications of a restriction that limits power output.
In the current draft of the schema, 'label', 'description' and 'comments' fields are available to describe the restriction with free text. This is intended to be expanded into a more comprehensive data model.
Attributes: label (str): Short label to indicate the type of operational restriction. description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None.

eya_def_tools.data_models.wind_farm.TurbineConfiguration
Specification of all details for a turbine configuration.
Attributes: turbine_id (Optional[str]): Unique identifier of the turbine specification. Default is None. label (str): Label of the turbine. description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None. location (Location): The horizontal spatial location of the turbine. hub_height (float): The hub height of the turbine. turbine_model_id (str): Unique identifier of the turbine model. restrictions (Optional[list[OperationalRestriction]]): List of operational restrictions at the turbine level. Default is None.

eya_def_tools.data_models.wind_resource.TurbineWindResourceAssessmentResults
Wind resource assessment results at turbine locations.
Attributes: wind_speed (list[Result]): Final long-term wind speed estimates at the turbine location(s). probability (Optional[list[Result]]): Final long-term probability distribution estimates at the turbine location(s), such as wind speed probability distributions or joint wind speed and direction frequency distributions. Default is None. wind_shear_exponent (Optional[list[Result]]): Final long-term power law wind shear exponent estimates at the turbine location(s). Default is None. temperature (Optional[list[Result]]): Final long-term temperature estimates at the turbine location(s). Default is None. air_density (Optional[list[Result]]): Final long-term air density estimates at the turbine location(s). Default is None.

eya_def_tools.data_models.wind_uncertainty.WindUncertaintyCategory
Category of a wind related uncertainty assessment.
Attributes: label (WindUncertaintyCategoryLabel(StrEnum)): Label of the wind related uncertainty assessment category. description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None. subcategories (list[WindUncertaintySubcategory]): Wind related uncertainty assessment subcategories that fall under the category. The subcategory objects include details and results at the subcategory level. category_results (list[Result]): Wind related uncertainty assessment category result(s) as dimensionless relative values.

eya_def_tools.data_models.spatial.Location
Specification of a horizontal location in space.
Attributes: location_id (Optional[str]): Unique identifier of the location. Default is None. label (Optional[str]): Label of the location. Default is None. description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None. x (float): Location x-coordinate (typically easing). y (float): Location y-coordinate (typically northing).

eya_def_tools.data_models.wind_uncertainty.WindUncertaintySubcategory
Subcategory of a wind related uncertainty assessment.
Attributes: label (WindUncertaintySubcategoryLabel(StrEnum)): Label of the wind related uncertainty subcategory. description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None. elements (Optional[list[WindUncertaintySubcategoryElement]]): Wind related uncertainty assessment elements that fall under the subcategory. A breakdown of wind related uncertainty subcategories into elements is optional and can be included only for a subset of the subcategories, as relevant. Whereas the categories and subcategories are fixed, the user may freely define element labels.
